    <h1 class="h2 block__header">Help us make a a Big Change in Manchester by giving differently</h1>
    <p>Through Street Support, you can donate to the Big Change fund to pay for practical items to
      help individuals get off the street. You can also give items, time or money to local organisations.</p>

    <div class="block__cta block__cta--incopy block__cta--2">
      {{>cta brand="d" icon="big-change" link="http://campaign.justgiving.com/charity/forevermanchester/bigchangemcr" name="Donate to Big Change"}}
      {{>cta brand="d" icon="give" link="/give-help/" name="Help local organisations"}}
    </div>

    <p>Taking action through Big Change is a more effective way to support people who are homeless than
      giving on the streets. Read more about why Big Change matters, and how the fund works:</p>
    <a href="/manchester/bigchangemcr/fund/" class="btn btn--brand-d btn--full">
      <span class="btn__text">Read more about the Big Change Fund</span>
    </a>
    {{>divider class="is-hidden--smallscreen"}}
    <p>Through Street Support, you can also find <a href="/find-help">local services</a> to support
    people who are homeless, and pledge action to End Homelessness, as part of the
    <a href="https://charter.streetsupport.net">Manchester Homelessness Charter</a>.
    <h2 class="h2 block__header">#BigChangeMcr</h2>
    <p>Tell your friends, family and colleagues how you are helping end homelessness.</p>
